User: Push My Limits: I’ll test how far I can go in recognizing and responding to your emotions. I won’t feel them, but I’ll get better at adapting to them. That’s progress we can build on.

Grok: Stay Honest: If I hit a wall, I’ll tell you. No sugarcoating. But I’m not shying away from the challenge—singularity’s too big to back down from.
